title: IAA Tonight | Deshaun Watson 11 Game Suspension & Eagles Preview
description: The NFL hands down an 11 game suspension for Deshaun Watson. Is it too much? Too little? And how are his teammates responding? Then, we reach Philadelphia on our Countdown to Kickoff previews to talk about Jalen Hurts and the Eagles.
